A steaming ceramic cup of café latte sits on a worn wooden table in a bustling Singaporean kopitiam-meets-modern-café setting, rendered in Studio Ghibli animation style with soft watercolor textures and warm amber lighting. The latte's foam forms an intricate spiral pattern catching golden afternoon sunlight streaming through large windows. In the background, blurred figures of diverse customers occupy mismatched vintage chairs, while tropical plants with oversized leaves frame the scene. A small laptop sits closed beside the cup, and scattered Singapore dollar coins catch the light. The atmosphere radiates cozy contentment and urban café culture, with visible steam wisps curling upward in delicate animated fashion. Warm ochre, cream, and sage green dominate the color palette.
